<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV59">
<l>aḷapparun taṉmaiya vūḻiyaṅ kaṅkulan taṇṇantuḻāyk</l>
<l>kuḷapperuṅ kātali ṉīḷiya vāyuḷa vōṅkumunnīr</l>
<l>vaḷapperu nāṭaṉ matucū taṉaṉeṉṉum valviṉaiyēṉ</l>
<l>taḷapperu nīṇmuṟu vaṟceyya vāya taṭamulaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Aeon[long] nights of a kind difficult to measure are there, as extensions</l>
<l>of [her] existing great love for the pretty cool Tulsi – for the large-breasted [girl]</l>
<l>with red mouth, with a very broad jasmine [tooth] smile, of me with harsh Karma,</l>
<l>who says: “the liberal great lord of the high ocean is Matucūtaṉaṉ”.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
